        "no_kd": null,
        "pertanyaan": "<p>Not so long after, the parade reached the rest post. It was the place for participants to draw a door prizes coupon and have some drinks.<\/p><p>After drawing a coupon, they continued to parade to their school as the final destination.<\/p><p>After returning to school, all participants took some rest while waiting for the door prizes announcement.<\/p><p>Acording to the text , the structure of recount that tells about the sequence of events is &nbsp;?<\/p>",
