        "jenis_penilaian": "pts",
        "tema_cls": null,
        "no_kd": null,
        "pertanyaan": "<p>Last month, my school held a camping activity at the mountain. It was my first experience, and I was very excited.<\/p><p>First, we built tents together with friends. After that, we cooked noodles and grilled fish. At night, we had a campfire. We sang songs, told stories, and played games. It was so much fun.<\/p><p>On the last day, we cleaned the area before going home. I was tired, but I felt happy because I got many new experiences.<\/p><p>Which sentence shows the orientation of the recount text?<\/p><p>&nbsp;<\/p>",
        "jawaban_a": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);\">First, we set up the tent with friends.<\/span><\/p>",
        "jawaban_b": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);\">Last month, my school held a camping event in the mountains.<\/span><\/p>",
        "jawaban_c": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(0,0,0);\">On the last day, we cleaned the area before going home.<\/span><\/p>",
