        "pertanyaan": "<p><strong>My Holiday in Yogyakarta<\/strong><\/p><p>Last holiday, I went to Yogyakarta with my family. We left Jakarta by train at night and arrived in the morning. On the first day, we visited Borobudur Temple. It was very beautiful and historical. I took many photos there.<\/p><p>The next day, we went to Malioboro Street. I bought some souvenirs and tried traditional food called <i>gudeg<\/i>. It was delicious. In the evening, we watched a Ramayana dance performance.<\/p><p>Where did the writer go on the last holiday?<\/p>",
